{"tid":2009489,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人入嚟，咩叫武字，止戈為武","createTime":"2020-05-09T18:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T08:02:32.000Z","uid":238660,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0ce6a383e2818b49f78352a3ca3ec188fc8337","tid":2009489,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:32:04.000Z","msg":"「汝欲和平，必先備戰。」<br />\n<br />\n勇武的「武」，就是「止戈為武」。<br />\n武力的目標，就是為了阻止更強橫的暴力，為了日後的安定、和平，即是「以戰促和」。<br />\n<br />\n武備不修，談何和平？"},{"pid":"72244eebc01461469f5de3b6c207d270b3205cfb","tid":2009489,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:32:49.000Z","msg":"何謂「武」<br />\n<br />\n武。從止,從戈。據甲骨文,人持戈行進,表示要動武。<br />\n<br />\n楚莊王曰,夫文止戈為武。又曰,夫武禁暴戢兵保大定功安民和財者也。&mdash;&mdash;《左氏春秋&middot;宣公十二年》<br />\n<br />\n武又指干戈軍旅之事 <br />\n德不厚而行武。&mdash;&mdash;《韓非子&middot;五蠹》"},{"pid":"03137307c7ed871531385d7e94893411fd545b93","tid":2009489,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"香港歷史頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/Hkhistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHkhistory&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpbyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=fc79dae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Hkhistory</a>"},{"pid":"cd509fd9b12d5a19bfec10f8820a6a976f006c52","tid":2009489,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:34:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4b0e5155ea256950575c333239a8cda525dffd6","tid":2009489,"uid":304858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:44:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eeeb254a0b7cf42f41c8a7a77b23a64057e55235","tid":2009489,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:46:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d10c07db2a95c55b767f9f72ec46b71491695e5b","tid":2009489,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T18:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /